title: Melvin or Ekeler, the Buy-Low Bengals, and Other Week 5 Matchups to Exploit | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck talk about the players who are too rich for their blood (4:20), players to buy low on (11:30), and contrarian players to start this week (20:00). Then they open the bargain bin and give out their Week 5 lineups (29:00).
